parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injury or fatalities, compromising the safety of vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
inconsistent airbag sensor detection
seat belts fail to lock
and airbags deploy unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning airbag sensors can lead to false warnings, inconsistent detection of occupants, and potentially, the failure of airbags to deploy in a crash, compromising the safety of vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbag warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
inconsistent airbag sensor detection
and airbags fail to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of seat belts to lock or function properly can lead to serious injury or fatalities in the event of a crash, compromising the safety of vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Seat belts fail to lock
and occupants are thrown into the windshield or injured in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Slipping or Failure to Engage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or failure to engage can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle loses power or stalls
the transmission fails to engage into gear
the vehicle jerks or lurches when shifting
the RPMs increase without corresponding acceleration
the vehicle downshifts unexpectedly
the transmission makes unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission lurching or jerking can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The transmission lurches or jerks when shifting gears
the vehicle hesitates or stalls
the transmission makes unusual noises
the vehicle surges or accelerates unexpectedly
the RPMs fluctuate erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure to downshift can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The transmission fails to downshift when necessary
the vehicle hesitates or stalls
the transmission makes unusual noises
the vehicle surges or accelerates unexpectedly
the RPMs fluctuate erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Acceleration Due to Cruise Control Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates independently
often when braking or slowing down
making a loud noise
and failing to respond to brake pedal input. In some cases
the cruise control unit disengages on its own or fails to turn on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electronic speed control system can cause the cruise control feature to fail to turn on or operate erratically, leading to driver inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The cruise control feature fails to turn on occasionally
or operates intermittently.
